  "prompt": "Which Bluetooth speakers are the best for under Rs 5k?",
  "response": "Finding a good Bluetooth speaker under Rs 5,000 can be a bit challenging, but there are several options that offer great sound quality, battery life, and features. Here are some of the best Bluetooth speakers under Rs 5,000 in 2023:\n\n1. **JBL Go 3**\n   - Compact and portable design\n   - IP67 waterproof and dustproof rating\n   - Punchy sound with deep bass\n   - Up to 5 hours of battery life\n\n2. **boAt Stone 1400 Mini**\n   - Rugged and durable build\n   - IPX5 water resistance\n   - Dual EQ Modes\n   - Up to 6 hours of battery life\n\n3. **Sony SRS-XB13**\n   - Extra Bass for deep sound\n   - IP67 water and dust proof\n   - Up to 16 hours of battery life\n   - Lightweight and portable design\n\n4. **Mi Portable Bluetooth Speaker (16W)**\n   - Powerful 16W sound output\n   - IPX7 waterproof rating\n   - Up to 13 hours of battery life\n   - Dual EQ modes\n\n5. **Anker Soundcore 2**\n   - 24 hours of playtime\n   - IPX7 water resistance\n   - Enhanced bass\n   - Robust build quality\n\n6. **TAGG Sonic Angle 1**\n   - 30W output with full-range drivers\n   - IPX7 waterproof rating\n   - Up to 8 hours of battery backup\n   - Modern design and lightweight\n\n7. **Infinity (JBL) Fuze 100**\n   - Deep Bass Sound\n   - Dual equalizer modes\n   - IPX7 Waterproof\n   - Up to 9 hours of playtime\n\nThese Bluetooth speakers are highly rated and well-regarded for their sound quality, durability, and features. Make sure to check for any ongoing discounts and offers to get the best deals.",
